title: Episode 2 w/ guest Ja Rule & Jadakiss
itunes:title: Episode 2 w/ guest Ja Rule & Jadakiss
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN drink up with legendary rapper's Jadakiss and Ja Rule and cover topics from touring with DMX, to their early beginnings before they hit it big. The conversation takes several twists and turns as the legendary MC's drink it up and talk as if the mics weren't on. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
